score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"呢啲野睇下就好，事在人為"},{"pid":"d4466003e29831a6f170340d151d6bf6de7d2fd8","tid":590171,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd4f4e39d34e0a987cbf925b3fa4a60e5ee9d501","tid":590171,"uid":65847,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"2011<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"好似話啲簽年年都係同一款<br />\n唔會變<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉<br />\n如果佢畀枝下簽我<br />\n叫我死咗條心未好囉<br />\n依家居然叫我唔好兒戲<br />\n同佢坦白、開心見誠講<br />\n又話要遵守承諾講嘢要算數<br />\n<br />\n之前我同佢講過<br />\n我唔會放棄唔會避開佢<br />\n我要珍惜同佢相處嘅機會<br />\n我要認識真實嘅佢<br />\n<br />\n依家我反而就退縮咗<br />\n軟弱咗<br />\n變得唔敢再搵人&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef3e7711ddbb70256a5fdbab81ad5afaceac275","tid":590171,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39db74ba2a803581abb49b82c6caf5e8bab68aa8","tid":590171,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"呢啲野睇下就好，事在人為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"事在人為<br />\n<br />\n睇咗而去做<br />\n都係人為呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e498c3cb8e7d1026596fca8b04f467bb35b0c03c","tid":590171,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"信果個都ON9"},{"pid":"4536bdc02f5bffa8af976392d762cf06d593aaed","tid":590171,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e498c3cb8e7d1026596fca8b04f467bb35b0c03c","tid":590171,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"信果個都ON9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T12:06:46.000Z","msg":"但人係迷失個陣需要一個可依靠嘅嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cf3435068d9db3762c4c940b74264082401849","tid":590171,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sco